quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  105,1,HAVE YOU not considered how your Lord dealt with the Army of the Elephant?¹
  105,2,Did He not confound their stratagem
  105,3,and send against them flocks of birds
  105,4,which pelted them with clay-stones
  105,5,so that they became like the withered stalks of plants which cattle had devoured